    "claim": "When `_claimPoolEarningsAndSellRewardTokens()` converts reward tokens into CNC, it immediately credits `earnedIntegral` with `receivedCnc_ / totalStaked` but does not advance `_rewardsMeta[_CNC_KEY].lastHoldings`. The next `poolCheckpoint()` therefore observes the same CNC sitting on the pool balance as fresh `cncEarned` and credits it a second time.",
